  "title": "Project Manager (Cyber Security) - Up to $6000",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles and Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>· Plan, manage, and deliver Cybersecurity related projects such as VAPT, Asset Discovery, Risk Assessment, GRC etc from initiation to closure.</p><p>· Develop project plans, timelines, milestones, and resource plans to ensure on-time and within-scope delivery.</p><p>· Track project progress, risks, issues, and dependencies, escalating where necessary.</p><p>· Prepare and present project status updates, reports, and dashboards to stakeholders and management.</p><p>· Manage and participate in IT risk assessment projects, including risk identification, impact and likelihood analysis, and risk treatment planning.</p><p>· Coordinate governance and compliance initiatives such as ISO 27001, IM8, PDPA, or other regulatory / industry frameworks.</p><p>· Work closely with IT, security, and business teams to assess controls and identify gaps.</p><p>· Ensure effective communication across all project stakeholders.<br /><br /><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><p>· Diploma or Degree from Computer Science / Cybersecurity related discipline of study.</p><p>· Minimum 3 years of working experience in project management involving IT risk, governance, or compliance.</p><p>· Good understanding of IT risk assessment methodologies and risk treatment processes.</p><p>· Familiarity with GRC frameworks and standards such as ISO 27001, NIST, COBIT, PDPA, or equivalent.</p><p>· Strong project management skills, including planning, scheduling, risk management, and reporting.</p><p>· Proven experience managing multiple workstreams and stakeholders.</p><p>· Strong knowledge of IT systems, networks, and security concepts.</p><p>· Good presentation skill and able to create presentation slides for related projects.</p><p>· Knowledge in compliance standards such as ISO27001, E26 & 27, Maritime IACS UR E26 & 27 and IM8 is advantageous.</p><p>· A collaborative team player with good communication skills and working attitude.<br /><br /><strong>Interested and suitable candidate kindly click quick apply. Resume will be forwarded to Stepfan Soon Yit</strong></p><p><strong>We regret that only suitable candidate will be notified.</strong></p><p><strong>GEMS Recruit/EA License : 23C1459</strong></p><p><strong>EA Personnel No : R24120893 (Stepfan Soon Yit)</strong></p>",
